text: Anastasia Valentinovna Voznesenskaya (; 27 July 1943 – 14 January 2022) was a Russian actress. She was awarded People's Artist of the Russian Federation in 1997.Анастасия Вознесенская на сайте МХТ Her career began in 1965. Her best known role was in Major Whirlwind.Энциклопедия кино (2010). Анастасия Валентиновна Вознесенская In late December 2021, Voznesenskaya tested positive for COVID-19. She died from the virus in Moscow on 14 January 2022, at the age of 78.Вдова Андрея Мягкова Анастасия Вознесенская умерла от COVID-19 ==References== Category:1943 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Moscow Category:Russian movie actors Category:Russian television actors Category:Russian stage actors Category:Actors from Moscow
